  26,66,Then We drowned the others
  26,67,Surely in this is a sign. Yet most of them would not believe
  26,68,"And your Lord is certainly the Almighty, Most Merciful"
  26,69,Relate to them ňĻO Prophetňļ the story of Abraham
  26,70,"when he questioned his father and his people, ‚ÄúWhat is that you worship ňĻbesides Godňļ?‚ÄĚ"
  26,71,"They replied, ‚ÄúWe worship idols, to which we are fully devoted.‚ÄĚ"
