  26,155,"ŠĻĘ√ĘliŠł• said, ‚ÄúHere is a camel. She will have her turn to drink as you have yours, each on an appointed day"
  26,156,"And do not ever touch her with harm, or you will be overtaken by the torment of a tremendous day.‚ÄĚ"
  26,157,"But they killed her, becoming regretful"
