  26,205,Imagine ňĻO Prophetňļ if We allowed them enjoyment for years
  26,206,then there came to them what they had been threatened with
  26,207,would that enjoyment be of any benefit to them ňĻat allňļ
  26,208,We have never destroyed a society without warners
  26,209,"to remind ňĻthemňļ, for We would never wrong ňĻanyoneňļ"
