  26,212,for they are strictly barred from ňĻevenňļ overhearing ňĻitňļ
  26,213,"So do not ever call upon any other god besides God, or you will be one of the punished"
  26,214,"And warn ňĻall, starting withňļ your closest relatives"
  26,215,and be gracious to the believers who follow you
  26,216,"But if they disobey you, say, ‚ÄúI am certainly free of what you do.‚ÄĚ"
  26,217,"Put your trust in the Almighty, Most Merciful"
